 This app uses Spotify playlists to play with. To access them, authentication is required. Note: not all songs have song preview - this is decided by Spotify. Therefore, a game can usually be played with fewer songs than there are on the selected playlist. We recommend that you use an English text-to-speech engine, as the information comes in English. Words in different languages can be difficult to recognize. Internet connection is needed while playing.
